&lt;p&gt;We are hiring this position to drive enterprise sales across our Employee Lifecycle business. You will work directly with CISOs, CHROs, and CIOs at some of the most influential organizations in the country to embed identity proofing and authentication into the moments that matter most—and you will be selling a solution that has measurable, defensible impact on fraud prevention, candidate experience, and operational cost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is high-stakes, high-impact work at the intersection of security, identity, and enterprise technology. If you&#39;re energized by complex problems, motivated by protecting people, and ready to bring your best to a category-defining company, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
